descriptionHtml:
ATTENTION: HOLIDAY SHOPPERS!
This Skyrim Shopping Mall has about 18 Shops contained within its walls.

Features:

* Bank with Vaults
* Clothing stores
* Hearthfire Emporium - contains necessary parts for your future homes
* Armor & Weapons
* Liquor Shop
* Gems and Jewelry
* Child Clothing
* Books
* The Wizard Apothecary
* A Cafe
* Health Spa with Hot and Cold pools
* Drugs & Torches
* Ore Mines Inc.
* Clutter Shop
* Produce Market
* Soul Gems
... and More!

version 1.0
USES ALL 3 DLC - Dragonborn, Hearthfire, & Dawnguard.

Located within walking distance of Whiterun City.
author: M7
